-# Indori Wuolingo
+# Indore02 (Iteration)
 
-> A gamified, enterprise-grade language learning platform for the Indori dialect — the vibrant, chaotic street Hindi of Indore, Madhya Pradesh.
+Milestone repo in the Indori-Wuolingo → IndiLingo series.
 
----
+This repository is a **milestone snapshot** in the public `Indore01` → `Indore12` build series.
 
-## What Is This?
+## Where to start (best candidate view)
 
-Indori Wuolingo brings the addictive lesson-streak mechanics of modern language apps to a deeply regional language experience. Users learn Indori slang, phrases, and culture through bite-sized exercises, earn XP, maintain streaks, and compete on global leaderboards.
+- **Final**: https://github.com/CRAJKUMARSINGH/Indore12
+- **Flagship dialect product**: https://github.com/CRAJKUMARSINGH/Indori-Wuolingo
 
-**Built for:** Language enthusiasts, cultural preservationists, Indore locals abroad, and anyone who wants to learn to say "Mhara Indore!" correctly.
+## What's inside
 
----
+- Monorepo (pnpm workspace)
+- `artifacts/api-server`: Express API server
+- `artifacts/indori-wuolingo`: Web app (React + Vite)
+- `lib/*`: OpenAPI spec + generated clients + DB schema
 
-## Features
-
-- Structured lesson tree with unlockable units
-- Multiple exercise types: translation, multiple choice, fill-in-the-blank, matching
-- XP and streak system
-- Global leaderboard
-- Per-user progress tracking
-- Platform stats dashboard
-- REST API with OpenAPI contract-first spec
-
