-## API Reference
-
-The OpenAPI spec lives at `lib/api-spec/openapi.yaml`. After editing it, regenerate clients:
-
-```bash
-pnpm --filter @workspace/api-spec run codegen
-```
-
-### Key Endpoints
-
-| Method | Path | Description |
-|---|---|---|
-| GET | /api/lessons | List all lessons |
-| GET | /api/lessons/:id | Lesson detail with exercises |
-| POST | /api/exercises/:id/submit | Submit an exercise answer |
-| GET | /api/leaderboard | Top users ranked by XP |
-| POST | /api/progress | Mark a lesson as complete |
-| GET | /api/stats/overview | Platform-wide stats |
-| GET | /api/stats/unit-progress | Per-unit completion |
